    {
        "content": "<p>Because it has a way to find <code>b</code> using unification. It won't search in the local context unless it is an instance implicit.</p>",
        "id": 530201048,
        "sender_full_name": "Robin Arnez",
        "timestamp": 1753208760
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>In other words, since the goal doesn't contain <code>f : Foo C c</code>, it won't find it. Since the goal contains <code>b : Bar C</code> it can find it.</p>",
        "id": 530201135,
        "sender_full_name": "Robin Arnez",
        "timestamp": 1753208800
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>thanks a lot, it starts to make sense :)</p>",
